content.rendered:
Directed by Devanshu Singh

Written by Manoj Kalwani

Cast Kriti Kharbanda(Aditi). Vikrant Massey(Sanjay). Gauahar Khan(Zubina). Iamrealmohsin(College Student). Jameel Khan(Amay). Vineet Kumar(Kanhaiya Lal Singh – Sanjay Father). Priyanshu Singh(Chotu). Udit Kapur(Delhi boy (as a different name)). Manoj Bakshi(Banwari). Yamini Das(Sarla Lal Singh- Sanjay Mother). Ankita Dubey(Shweta). Rajendra Bhatia(Tau). Govind Pandey(Aditi’s father). Bhupesh Singh(Mishra). Sumit Chandra(Waiter at the BAR). Shubham Pandey(Theatre Crew 6). Sonakshi Batra(Sneha). Shivani Sopori(Mrs. Gupta (as Shivaani Sopuri)). Avinash Raj Sharma(Arpit). Anupam Mishra(Theatre crew). Ankita Dubey(Shweta (archive footage)). Sumit Suri(Vivek). Mahesh Chandra Deva(Chottu’s man (as Mahesh Deva)). Kapil Tilhari(Office Recruiter 3). Vinod Saroj(Constable). Sushmita Mehta(Sanjay’s Friend). Nadeem Sheikh(Police Inspector). Rashmi Ruby Verma(Sanjay’s Bua). Akhilesh Tripathi(Sanjay’s Friend).Ehsan Mohammadi. Bhupendra Shahi(Theatre Director). Abhitosh Singh Rajput(Office friend)

Languages Hindi

Producers Tanmay Bhat. Arun Singh Dikky. Sumit Khurana. Vinit Masram. Sameer Siddiqui. Satyanshu Singh. Ajay R. Yadav.

Production Zee Studios
